<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="utf-8"/>
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1"/>
    <title>Task Manager - ElixiHub</title>
    <style>
        body {
            font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, 'Segoe UI', Roboto, Oxygen, Ubuntu, Cantarell, sans-serif;
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #667eea 0%, #764ba2 100%);
            min-height: 100vh;
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            justify-content: center;
        }
        .container {
            background: white;
            padding: 3rem;
            border-radius: 20px;
            box-shadow: 0 20px 40px rgba(0,0,0,0.1);
            text-align: center;
            max-width: 500px;
        }
        h1 {
            color: #333;
            margin-bottom: 1rem;
            font-size: 2.5rem;
        }
        .subtitle {
            color: #666;
            margin-bottom: 2rem;
            font-size: 1.2rem;
        }
        .button {
            display: inline-block;
            background: #667eea;
            color: white;
            padding: 1rem 2rem;
            text-decoration: none;
            border-radius: 10px;
            font-weight: 500;
            transition: transform 0.2s;
            margin: 0.5rem;
        }
        .button:hover {
            transform: translateY(-2px);
        }
        .features {
            margin-top: 2rem;
            text-align: left;
        }
        .feature {
            margin: 1rem 0;
            padding: 1rem;
            background: #f8f9fa;
            border-radius: 10px;
        }
        .feature h3 {
            margin: 0 0 0.5rem 0;
            color: #333;
        }
        .feature p {
            margin: 0;
            color: #666;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="container">
        <h1>Task Manager</h1>
        <p class="subtitle">Powerful task management for ElixiHub</p>
        
        <a href="/app" class="button">Open Task Manager</a>
        <a href="/api/tasks" class="button">API Documentation</a>
        <a href="http://localhost:4005/sso/auth?app_id=task_manager&return_to=http%3A//localhost%3A4010/sso/authenticate" class="button">Login with ElixiHub</a>
        
        <div class="features">
            <div class="feature">
                <h3>üîê Secure Authentication</h3>
                <p>Integrated with ElixiHub's JWT authentication system</p>
            </div>
            <div class="feature">
                <h3>üìù Task Management</h3>
                <p>Create, organize, and track tasks with priorities and due dates</p>
            </div>
            <div class="feature">
                <h3>ü§ñ AI Integration</h3>
                <p>MCP server provides tools for AI agents to manage tasks</p>
            </div>
            <div class="feature">
                <h3>üîÑ Real-time Updates</h3>
                <p>Phoenix LiveView provides instant updates across all users</p>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</body>
</html>